data.meta_description: AllisoNews, the employee newsletter of Allison Division (1941-1971), features news concerning Allison employees' work and recreation. It was published bi-monthly until the early 1960s when it became a monthly publication. There is a gap in publication November 1945-May 1946 due to closure during GM strikes.
